'''Tawntoom''' was the province<ref name="TEGtPaM" /><ref name="Geonosis and the Outer Rim Worlds">''[[Geonosis and the Outer Rim Worlds]]''</ref> of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Roon/Legends|Roon]] and was ruled by [[Governor/Legends|Governor]] [[Bisad Koong]] until [[15 BBY/Legends|15 BBY]]. Its [[Capital/Legends|capital]] [[City/Legends|city]], [[Fortress of Tawntoom]], was located inside a caldera.

